Description:
    Generates the migration files to create database tables for Generalis models.

Example:
    bin/rails generate generalis:migrations

    This will create:                                                                                                                                        14:38:52
      db/migrate/00000000000000_create_ledger_accounts.rb
      db/migrate/00000000000000_create_ledger_entries.rb
      db/migrate/00000000000000_create_ledger_operations.rb
      db/migrate/00000000000000_create_ledger_links.rb
